{"title":"JavaWeb学习之路（二）——环境配置与项目创建","slug":"JavaWeb学习之路（二）——环境配置与项目创建","date":"2021-05-01T04:19:29.000Z","updated":"2021-05-01T05:36:43.406Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/JavaWeb学习之路（二）——环境配置与项目创建.json","excerpt":null,"covers":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"学习开发环境\">学习开发环境</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>使用IDE : IDEA</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501122600387.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501122600387\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501122600387</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>使用学生身份可免费获得许可证</p></li>\r\n<li><p>Tomcat 9</p></li>\r\n<li><p>Maven 3.8</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"项目基本环境配置\">项目基本环境配置</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"java配置\">Java配置</h3>\r\n<p>略过。。</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"maven配置\">Maven配置</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>从官网下载压缩包，并解压到某个文件夹中。创建<code>maven-repo</code>文件夹作为本地参考存放组件。</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501123921278.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501123921278\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501123921278</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501123817964.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501123817964\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501123817964</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>系统环境变量配置</p>\r\n<p>M2_HOME和Path</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501124314588.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501124314588\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501124314588</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<h3 id=\"tomcat配置\">Tomcat配置</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>下载</p></li>\r\n<li><p>建议将conf/logging.properties 下部分编码修改为GBK</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501124602582.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501124602582\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501124602582</figcaption>\r\n</figure></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"使用idea创建项目\">使用IDEA创建项目</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>从原型创建</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501123142077.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501123142077\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501123142077</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>配置项目信息</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501123309805.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501123309805\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501123309805</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Maven路径配置</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501123442362.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501123442362\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501123442362</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>完成</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501124807711.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501124807711\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501124807711</figcaption>\r\n</figure></li>\r\n<li><p>设置Tomcat服务器</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501125013722.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501125013722\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501125013722</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501125242109.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501125242109\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501125242109</figcaption>\r\n</figure></li>\r\n<li><p>调整至规范目录结构</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501130029893.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501130029893\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501130029893</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501125834777.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501125834777\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501125834777</figcaption>\r\n</figure></li>\r\n<li><p>servlet 配置</p>\r\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Servlet1</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">HttpServlet</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 输入要继承的内容后，点击提示，选择添加Maven依赖项</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501131202357.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501131202357\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501131202357</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501131354267.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501131354267\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501131354267</figcaption>\r\n</figure></li>\r\n<li><p>之后新建选择Servlet即可</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501131442924.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501131442924\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501131442924</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501131606939.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501131606939\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501131606939</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>它会帮助我们自动填写<code>&lt;servlet&gt;</code>标签,我们只要添加<code>&lt;servlet-mapping&gt;</code>标签内容即可。</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501131723052.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501131723052\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501131723052</figcaption>\r\n</figure></li>\r\n<li><p>即重写get、post等方法了</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501131840514.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501131840514\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501131840514</figcaption>\r\n</figure></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n","more":"<h2 id=\"学习开发环境\">学习开发环境</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><p>使用IDE : IDEA</p>\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"../img/image-20210501122600387.png\"\r\nalt=\"image-20210501122600387\" />\r\n<figcaption aria-hidden=\"true\">image-20210501122600387</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>使用学生身份可免费获得许可证</p></li>\r\n<li><p>Tomcat 9</p></li>\r\n<li><p>Maven 3.8</p></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 id=\"项目基本环境配置\">项目基本环境配置</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"java配置\">Java配置</h3>\r\n<p>略过。。</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"maven配置\">Maven配置</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>从官网下载压缩包，并解压到某个文件夹中。创建<code>maven-repo</c